               <head>A Persian manuscript on the history of India bound together with several
                  printed Arabic, Persian, and Hindustani linguistic texts.</head>
               <msContents>

                  <summary>This volume primarily contains a manuscript entitled <title
                        xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7403">Nasab al-Ansāb</title> (Lineage of
                     the Ancestors), which recounts a general history of India. Several printed
                     linguistic texts append the volume.</summary>
               </msContents>
